description:
Good morning and welcome to the ride! Stop the worry because God got you. It's Taco Tuesday. The Chief Love Officer is in rare form today. R. Kelly is facing life in prison for all of his crimes. Is there such a thing as "election integrity" or nah? The weed industry has been making the heist of the century through acquisition and acquisition of employees from different industries. Pimpin' hot because he got on his microwave jacket! Something happened with an Ohio State Football player and Steve has a real question. Today in Closing Remarks, Steve breaks down life with a simple 10/90 formula.
